quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  34,46,"(Yaa Muhammad!) jedhi: “kan ani isin gorsu waan tokko qofattiInnis akka cimdiifi kophaanis Allaahf dhaabattanii, ergasii saahiba keessan (Muhammaditti) maraatummaan tokkollee hin jiru jechuu xiinxaltaniifiInni akeekkachiisaa adabbii cimaa dura isiniif (ergame) malee waan biraa hin taane"
  34,47,"Jedhi: “mindaa irraa wanti ani isin gaafadhe (yoo jiraates) inni isinumaafiMindaan kiyyas Rabbi irratti malee hin taaneInnis waan hunda irratti hirmaataa argaadha.”"
  34,48,"“Dhugumatti, Rabbiin kiyya dhugaa ni buusa(Inni) beekaa iccitiiwwan hundaati” jedhiin"
  34,49,“Dhugaan dhufe; sobni (taaytaa isaa) hin jalqabu; hin deebi’us” jedhiin
  34,50,"“Yoon jalladhes, kan ani jalladhu lubbuu kiyya irrattiYoon karaa qajeelaa qabadhes, waan Rabbiin kiyya gara kiyyatti erguuniInni dhugumatti dhagayaa, dhihaataadha” jedhi"
  34,51,"(Yaa Mohammad SAW!) odoo yeroo isaan (ibidda arganii) rifatan agartee, (silaa waan guddaa agarta)Iddoon itti bahanis (isaaniif) hin jiruIddoo dhihoo irraa qabamanii jiru"
  34,52,(Guyyaa Qiyaamaa) “Isatti amannee jirra” jedhuIddoo fagoo (biyya addunyaa) irraa (iimaana) fudhachuun akkamitti isaaniif mijjata
  34,53,"Dhugumatti, kana dura isatti kafaranii turanIddoo fagoo ta’e irraa (tilmaamaan) haasawa darbatu"
  34,54,"Gidduu isaaniitiifi gidduu waan isaan fedhaniitti akkuma san dura fakkaattota isaanii irratti godhametti haguuggiin godhamee jira; Dhugumatti, isaan shakkii cimaa keessatti ta’anii jiru"